column5: Oh geez! My eyeballs must not be working today. :)
I have also had a "cold" for ~ 20 years. I usually say "I don't want to shake hands just in case to avoid sharing germs" with a smile and usually people laugh and agree with me.
Apologies, I didn't realize they were different things.
Thank you! Have a great vacation.
